Name:           Demon Lord
Short Name:     lord
Level Required: 28

Description:
  An extremely powerful creature from the lower Planes, the Demon Lord
  uses all attacks of the Greater Demon. In addition, it can cause
  its foes to flee in sheer terror.

Commands:
  - summon lord:    Summons it to you         (costs 300 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cter <monster>: Makes <monster> flee      (costs 50 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban lord:       Banishes it               (costs 40 sp)
